|   - Cut                                                      |         Ctrl+X             |
|   - Copy                                                     |         Ctrl+C             |
|   - Paste                                                    |         Ctrl+V             |
|                                                              |                            |
|   - Rename                                                   |         F2                 |
|   - Rename Inline                                            |         Shift+F2           |
|                                                              |                            |
|   - Delete                                                   |         Shift+Delete       |
|                                                              |                            |
|   - New Folder                                               |         F10                |
|   - New File                                                 |         Ctrl+Shift+N       |
|                                                              |                            |
|   - Toggle Icon and List mode                                |         Ctrl+Shift+V       |
